'''''Chazaliella''''' is a [[genus]] of [[flowering plant]]s in the [[Family (biology)|family]] [[Rubiaceae]].<ref>Petit, Ernest Marie Antoine. 1975.  Kew Bulletin 30: 268.</ref> It has about 20 species native to tropical [[Africa]] from [[Liberia]] to [[Tanzania]] and south to [[Zimbabwe]].<ref name="WCSP">{{cite web|url=http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/qsearch.do?plantName=Chazaliella|title=''Chazaliella'' in the World Checklist of Rubiaceae|accessdate=June 2014}}</ref>

